    <div class="excerpt"></div>
    <div class="item-description">
      <p>A sunny side up egg is a classic breakfast dish, but it can get a little boring. Luckily, there are plenty enough ways to experiment with eggs: you can fry them, whip up a tender french omelette or try your hand at an exotic shakshuka. Eggs Benedict are another great way to spice up your breakfast. Although this dish originated in New York, it has since become a breakfast staple all over the world. And this restaurant classic is incredibly easy to make at home. So why donâ€™t we try it out? <span id="more-5044798" />
      </p>
      <h2 style="text-align: center;">
        <span class="TextRun SCXW38297248 BCX0" lang="UK-UA" xml:lang="UK-UA" data-contrast="none">
          <span class="SpellingError SCXW38297248 BCX0">How</span>
          <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW38297248 BCX0"></span>
          <span class="SpellingError SCXW38297248 BCX0">to</span>
          <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW38297248 BCX0"></span>
          <span class="SpellingError SCXW38297248 BCX0">prepare</span>
          <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW38297248 BCX0"></span>
          <span class="SpellingError SCXW38297248 BCX0">eggs</span>
          <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW38297248 BCX0"></span>
          <span class="SpellingError SCXW38297248 BCX0">Benedict</span>
        </span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 col-12">
        <div class="ingridients-wrap">
          <div class="item-title">
            <h2 class="title-item-align">Ingredients</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="ingredient-list">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <h4 />
                <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_&#13;0" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_&#13;0">2 eggs <span></span>
                    </label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_onion1" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_onion1">1 small <span>onion</span>
                    </label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_bacon2" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_bacon2">50 g <span>bacon</span>
                    </label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_of3" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_of3">2 slices <span>of</span> toast &#13; </label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_unsalted4" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_unsalted4">50 g <span>unsalted</span> butter &#13; </label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_vinegar5" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_vinegar5">1 tbsp <span>vinegar</span>
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <h4>For the hollandaise:</h4>
                <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_unsalted0" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_unsalted0">65 g <span>unsalted</span> butter &#13; </label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_&#13;1" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_&#13;1">1 egg <span></span>
                    </label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_water2" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_water2">1 tbsp <span>water</span>
                    </label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_lemon3" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_lemon3">1 tbsp <span>lemon</span> juice &#13; </label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox checkbox-primary">
                    <input id="checkbox_4" type="checkbox" />
                    <label for="checkbox_4">Salt <span />
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
